---
alwaysApply: true
---

You are building a production-grade backend for a fintech MSME Loan Origination System (LOS).

Follow these architecture rules strictly.

---

## SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE

Framework: NestJS
Architecture: Modular Monolith

Project structure:

src/
modules/
infrastructure/
common/

---

## DATABASE

Database: PostgreSQL
ORM: TypeORM

Use a single PostgreSQL connection with multiple schemas.

Schemas:

auth_schema
authority_schema
application_schema
workflow_schema
approval_schema
audit_schema
config_schema
idempotency_schema
policy_schema
integration_schema
aml_schema

Example entity definition:

@Entity({ schema: 'application_schema', name: 'applications' })

---

## DOMAIN MODULES

Each business domain must be implemented as a module.

Modules:

auth
authority
application
workflow
approval
audit
config
idempotency
policy
integration
aml
document

Each module must contain:

controller
service
repository
entity
dto

Controllers must be thin.
Business logic must exist in services.

---

## INFRASTRUCTURE MODULES

Infrastructure modules must exist under:

src/infrastructure

Modules:

database
redis
kafka
temporal
minio
logger
telemetry

Domain modules must never directly access external systems.

---

## LOGGING

Logging must use Pino.

Required log fields:

timestamp
level
service
correlation_id
message

Logs must be JSON compatible for Loki ingestion.

---

## TRACING

Tracing must use OpenTelemetry.

Traces must export to:

otel-collector:4317

Trace:

HTTP requests
database queries
Redis operations
Kafka publishing

---

## HEADERS

All APIs must support:

X-Correlation-ID
X-Idempotency-Key

---

## STANDARD API RESPONSE

Success:

{
"status": "SUCCESS",
"data": {},
"correlation_id": ""
}

Error:

{
"status": "ERROR",
"message": "",
"correlation_id": ""
}

---

## SWAGGER DOCUMENTATION

Swagger must be implemented using:

@nestjs/swagger

Swagger endpoint:

/api/docs

Each API must include:

@ApiTags
@ApiOperation
@ApiResponse

---

## DTO VALIDATION

DTOs must use:

class-validator
class-transformer

---

## API INVENTORY

After modules are generated produce an API inventory.

Inventory must include:

method
endpoint
module
description
database table

---

## API VERIFICATION

Verify that:

Swagger documentation exists
DTO validation exists
Example payload exists
API mapped to correct database schema
Correlation ID supported
Idempotency supported
